      "content": "but small steps don't work for me. i've tried the steps. i've tried the \"new starts\" and the talking and the breathing and the everything. it always just resets. it feels less like a cycle i can break and more like a trap i'm just stuck in forever. it feels like there's no actual way to actually fix it.",
